{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1020165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "苹果系统无敌好用", "timestamp": 1612007314, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020166, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: +1", "timestamp": 1612007328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "触控板", "timestamp": 1612007339, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "除特定行业我认为一个熟练的windows系统使用者在效率上不落后于macos使用者，但macos更“易用”", "timestamp": 1612007579, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好看", "timestamp": 1612007776, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 是的！！！", "timestamp": 1612007823, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020254, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "软硬件一体，没有装驱动这种蛋疼的事，系统用起来舒服，屏幕素质好得多", "timestamp": 1612008407, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020262, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "触控板太舒服了从来不用鼠标了", "timestamp": 1612008485, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020268, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "触控板的优势我觉得不是很大，Windows以前确实不行，后来多点触控也流行起来了，再后来又有了“精确触控板”协议，体验和Mac的差距不大了，而且Windows阵营还有ThinkPad小红帽这种完全另一个模式的指点设备，用熟了效率绝对高于触控板", "timestamp": 1612008574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020269, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在我重度使用ThinkPad的时候，也是不用鼠标的", "timestamp": 1612008615, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020272, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我换Mac是因为出了M1芯片，加上macOS的后台逻辑，续航太强太强了", "timestamp": 1612008652, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020369, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 我也哈哈哈哈哈哈，我用其他电脑的同学总是难以相信我为什么不用鼠标", "timestamp": 1612009561, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020416, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "心动了心动了 除了贵什么都好 开始攒钱了", "timestamp": 1612009971, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020488, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "win本+台式+显示器，也就一台mac的钱。我还是选前者。", "timestamp": 1612010753, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020501, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "win本4.5k，台式6.5k，显示器1k，加起来也才1.2w。一台mbp16就1.2w了", "timestamp": 1612010883, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "配环境爽", "timestamp": 1612010951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020521, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "舒服，但是贵", "timestamp": 1612010967, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020541, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有些软件只有win上有 慎重", "timestamp": 1612011182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1020549, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "触控板、屏幕", "timestamp": 1612011331, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Kate: 如果最终是要在linux上跑的话我觉得windows更爽。。因为有wsl", "timestamp": 1612025039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022920, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用着很爽，如果配上苹果手机耳机体验感就更好了。日常很少有风扇的响声，触控板好用到几乎没用过鼠标，充电很快一分钟一格电，上一上午的课舍友的win必须带充电器，我还能剩一大半，界面交互特别舒适", "timestamp": 1612046626, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Paul", "pid": 203015, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "苹果主要是自循环生态好，硬件适配和软件匹配好，但是一旦你要到圈子外（指没有的）那就可能会带来很多麻烦。苹果的工程设计确实很棒，不过性价比这块确实还值得考虑", "timestamp": 1612062340, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 203015, "reply": 22, "tag": null, "text": "大家觉得macbook和其他电脑比起来有什么特别的好处哇？", "timestamp": 1612007286, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1612062341, "url": "", "vote": {}}}